import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='ignore')
    grouped_data = data.groupby(['site', 'year'])['yield'].mean().reset_index()
    grouped_data['site_year'] = grouped_data['site'] + ' - ' + grouped_data['year'].astype(str)
    
    ax = grouped_data.plot.bar(x='site_year', y='yield', legend=False)
    ax.set_ylabel('Average Yield')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.title('What is the average yield of barley across all sites and years?', wrap=True)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    avg_yield_by_variety = data.groupby('variety')['yield'].mean()
    avg_yield_by_variety.plot(kind='bar')
    
    plt.xlabel('Variety')
    plt.ylabel('Average Yield')
    plt.title('Which variety of barley has the highest yield on average?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    max_avg_yield = avg_yield_by_variety.max()
    max_variety = avg_yield_by_variety.idxmax()
    plt.axhline(max_avg_yield, color='r', linestyle='--', label=f'Max Avg Yield: {max_variety} ({max_avg_yield:.2f})')
    plt.legend()
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    sites = data['site'].unique()
    for site in sites:
        site_data = data[data['site'] == site]['yield']
        plt.hist(site_data, alpha=0.5, label=site)
    plt.xlabel('Yield')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.legend(title='Site')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title('What is the distribution of yield for each site?')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
